            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Line</strong> a baking tray with tin foil or baking paper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Divide</strong> the mixture into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">(12)</span> even portions and using wet hands, shape them into balls</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> them to the baking tray and place in the oven for 12-15 min, or until the outsides are golden&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
