    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, boil a kettle for step 7</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> and finely chop the onion<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Return</strong> the mushroom pan to a medium-high heat with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> of olive oil</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the onions with a pinch of salt and the remaining garlic and fry for 2-3 min, or until the onions are translucent</p>",
      "order": 5,
