      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the canned tomatoes, soy sauce, balsamic vinegar, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tsp)</span> of sugar and 1/4 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(1/2 tsp)</span> of pepper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Increase</strong> the heat to high and bring to a boil</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> boiling, reduce the heat to low and simmer gently for 8-10 min with a lid, until thickened</p>",
